Designing and Implementing UI/UX

Objective:
The goal of Task 2 was to design and implement user interface (UI) and user experience (UX) components for the project.

Activities:

Design Preparation (Days 10-12):

Studied UI/UX principles and best practices.
Used Figma and Adobe XD for wireframing and mockups, establishing a solid foundation for UI/UX layout and design.

Implement UI Components (Days 13-15):

Converted wireframes and mockups into Android layouts.
Implemented basic UI components, such as buttons, text fields, and navigation elements, ensuring smooth user interactions.

Integrate Design (Days 16-18):

Applied styles and themes to match design specifications.
Set up a responsive layout to adapt to different screen sizes, enhancing the user experience across devices.

Deliverables:

All UI/UX components have been implemented and pushed to this repository.
A LinkedIn post has been created to showcase the completed UI/UX design and integration.
